1671476252794%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=Rq0KpPxW9tA6I4%2Fq6ambdfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=69bfa860\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sjkorean/photos/a.173528062733808.46404.115930788493536/771671476252794/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n【韓國節慶】 (兒冬至)<br />\n<br />\n冬至為一年四季中白晝最短、夜晚最漫長的一天。韓國習俗是在冬至時將紅豆煮得像粥一般濃稠，吃美味的팥죽(紅豆粥)，因為據說紅色可以擊退惡鬼；在紅豆粥中加入跟自己年紀一樣數量的湯圓，表示自己又增長了一歲。<br />\n<br />\n但是今年的冬至韓國不吃紅豆粥，而是改吃팥떡(紅豆年糕)。因為今年是&rdquo;애동지&rdquo; (兒冬至)的緣故。<br />\n<br />\n為什麼呢? 什麼是&quot;애동지&rdquo; (兒冬至)?<br />\n<br />\n冬至一般是每年國曆的12月22~23日，如果是落在農曆11月初~上旬期間，就稱為애동지(兒冬至)；若是在11月中旬就是중동지(中冬至)，而如果是在11月下旬的話，就是노동지(老冬至)。<br />\n<br />\n今年的冬至正好是農曆11月初1，所以是兒冬至。<br />\n<br />\n韓國有一說，如果在兒冬至吃紅豆粥的話，對10歲以下的小孩子會有不好的事情發生。在韓國有位삼신할머니(三神娘娘)，類似於台灣的註生娘娘，逢產子或是為孩子祈福時便會祭拜三神娘娘。不過如果吃了紅豆粥驅鬼，就會連三神娘娘都一起趕走，那這樣三神娘娘就沒辦法保護小孩了。<br />\n<br />\n所以當兒冬至時，韓國家裡有小孩的家庭，為了小孩的關係而要改吃紅豆年糕，就是這個緣故。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://archive.is/0BQu7/6e1d5bccf5b7b3466c3166b7bf1650c02c8e70c0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.is%2F0BQu7%2F6e1d5bccf5b7b3466c3166b7bf1650c02c8e70c0&h=2bf2a1df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3517333836b0157d68f0acca9c4aa9c7323a8d23","tid":507012,"uid":43189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T10:46:37.000Z","msg":"JR狗講兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40e601de1f9be23823603f75e3e5322e2bab4654","tid":507012,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T10:59:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實全世界都有做冬<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cup.com.hk/2017/12/21/winter-solstice-celebrate/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2Fwinter-solstice-celebrate%2F&d=Rq0KpPxW9tA6I4%2Fq6ambdfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=076a9c64\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cup.com.hk/2017/12/21/winter-solstice-celebrate/</a></blockquote>原來英格蘭、愛爾蘭、西班牙都有！<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實聖誕節本身係羅馬嘅冬至"},{"pid":"9d9b9ce893f42f98cf09afdb594db24541b98973","tid":507012,"uid":32832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T11:09:14.000Z","msg":"全球60億都係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e357a1af620e36bfa2f834d5484ac5fb78983cd4","tid":507012,"uid":164167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eeb3354758d09e8ebcbe4a05dd5a588bb7c5cbb0","tid":507012,"uid":14758,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T19:05:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://c.blog.xuite.net/c/e/9/f/18362079/blog_1168435/txt/29493907/8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fc.blog.xuite.net%2Fc%2Fe%2F9%2Ff%2F18362079%2Fblog_1168435%2Ftxt%2F29493907%2F8.jpg&h=9769d275&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有啲味<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T17:44:32.000Z","msg":"日本真心on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ea4982941ec6c9ba0b8511b45c44d784c798a48","tid":507012,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T05:45:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>JR狗講兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/810/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/140426_b2644c62ffbe6ee9c87695e7aa4566f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F810%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F140426_b2644c62ffbe6ee9c87695e7aa4566f1.jpg&h=dbe32679&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0236ed89ea556ec2eefd4c69574fe665a90e579","tid":507012,"uid":4180